headline: United Becomes Official Airline Partner of the Golden State Valkyries, the WNBA's Newest Expansion Team
summary: United Airlines and the Golden State Valkyries today announced a multi-year sponsorship with United as founding partner and the organization's official airline ahead of the Valkyries' inaugural season at the Chase Center.
